bird_exporter exports BIRD routing daemon metrics in Prometheus format.

It connects to the BIRD control socket and exports per-protocol
statistics including BGP session state, OSPF neighbors, prefix counts,
uptime, and import/export filters.

Supports BIRD 1.x and BIRD 2.x (use -bird.v2 flag for version 2+).

WWW: https://github.com/czerwonk/bird_exporter
